thread.title: Susan

author: Susan
title: Susan
text:
The good- user friendly form and printout of mailing label and postage. Check came fast.
The not-so-good my initial email was slowly answered with a canned reply that didn't answer my question. Phone message left was never answered. BUT , this was after student book-buying time, so maybe they were all on vacation. Lastly, I typed in my book list over several days, and in between, it would update a book to a more recent edition. I kept having to change them back. YES , I would sell here again.
